  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To confirm that patients who receive the Star-Close vascular closure system (VCS) can safely
      ambulate within 30 minutes of catheterization.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      To confirm that patients who receive the Star-Close vascular closure system (VCS) after
      diagnostic cardiac catheterization can safely ambulate within 30 minutes of catheterization.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
